description: Nyuma y’amezi atandatu,umwana atangira guhabwa imfashabere; konsa bigako-meza kugeza ate imyaka ibiri cyangwa irenga kuko amashereka atanga intun-gamubiri, ingufu kandi akarinda umwana indwara.
